Markers and inks—
I planned on adding so much black to this so i could breathe easier (lol) but before i could even submit this assignment, i spilled water on it while fighting a friend on the phone. The marker ink swam a bit in there. 
Had a moment with myself right there. I didn’t cry but yeah it was hard. 
Nextly, Held this in my hand and fought my ‘the world is ending and everything is about to die’ thoughts and went ahead with it. Submitted it as it is. Added some black tape to it, got good marks to be honest but i feel ‘mehh’ about this. Thought I’ll collage it up and throw it in here mehhh.
